text: Michelle Rojas is an American voice actress. She is known for voicing Kanan Matsuura in Love Live! Sunshine!!, Wendy in Show by Rock!!, Yatogami in Date A Live, Mini (Gemini) in Fairy Tail, Nashiro Yasuhisa in Tokyo Ghoul and Jabari Smith in Prism Dreamers.
